Summary:
- CodeWise is a Supabase-backed TanStack Start app for AI-assisted DSA learning.
- Review and practice flows are implemented as server functions in `src/lib/`.
- Billing is Paddle-based and environment-aware.
- The refined `.claude/rules/` files are the best generated memory surface in this repo.
